      <title>迪奥包袋风波过后，韩国总统支持率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/south-korean-president-sees-support-slide-after-dior-bag-uproar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈的支持率跌至 4 月份以来的最低水平，因第一夫人是否可能不当收到奢侈名牌包的质疑不断升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/south-korean-president-sees-support-slide-after-dior-bag-uproar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 02:50:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩在“战争准备”中推动海军力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/kim-jong-un-makes-push-for-naval-might-in-war-preparations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩在访问韩国一座岛屿附近的海军造船厂时呼吁加强“战争准备”，该岛曾经是致命对抗的场所，这加剧了他最近使用的好战言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/kim-jong-un-makes-push-for-naval-might-in-war-preparations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 01:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国尝试发放 1,000 英镑签约奖金以解决儿童保育员短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/uk-tries-1-000-sign-on-bonus-to-fix-childcare-worker-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)政府将提供价值1,000英镑(1,270美元)的签约奖金，以吸引人们从事儿童保育工作，因为政府试图解决长期的人员短缺问题，这种短缺可能会破坏总理为工薪家庭提供更多支持的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/uk-tries-1-000-sign-on-bonus-to-fix-childcare-worker-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登团队表示将对美军死亡事件做出有针对性的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/the-world-waits-as-biden-telegraphs-attack-on-iran-backed-groups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登毫不掩饰他对伊朗支持的一个组织发动多次袭击的意图，该组织上周杀死了三名美国士兵，这一战略让他受到批评，认为他放弃了出其不意的元素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/the-world-waits-as-biden-telegraphs-attack-on-iran-backed-groups</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 23:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
