      <title>关键制裁顾问离开美国财政部前往私营部门工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/key-sanctions-adviser-leaves-us-treasury-for-private-sector-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责制裁和金融犯罪政策的财政部官员伊丽莎白·罗森伯格(Elizabeth Rosenberg)将前往私营部门工作。]]></description>
