      <title>拜登争取工会汽车工人与特朗普争夺密歇根州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/biden-woos-union-auto-workers-in-battle-with-trump-for-michigan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图利用他最近获得美国汽车工人联合会的支持，与成员一起在关键的摇摆州密歇根州的一家电话银行做志愿者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/biden-woos-union-auto-workers-in-battle-with-trump-for-michigan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 22:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港新国安法给金融中心带来焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hong-kong-s-new-security-law-brings-fresh-anxiety-to-finance-hub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港特首李家超过去一年一直在努力重振因疫情限制措施和中国经济放缓而遭受重创的香港商业环境。他颁布国内安全法的决定可能会破坏这些努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hong-kong-s-new-security-law-brings-fresh-anxiety-to-finance-hub</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在委内瑞拉紧张局势升级之际，美国官员将前往波哥大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-officials-to-travel-to-bogota-amid-rising-venezuela-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与邻国委内瑞拉的紧张关系日益加剧，拜登政府高级官员将于下周在波哥大与哥伦比亚官员举行高级别会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-officials-to-travel-to-bogota-amid-rising-venezuela-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 20:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰陆军参谋长因战争努力与泽连斯基产生分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/ukraine-s-army-chief-says-strategy-overhaul-is-needed-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰最高将领加倍努力与总统泽连斯基就军事领导权问题展开对抗，在抗击俄罗斯入侵战争的关键时刻加剧了基辅的权力斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/ukraine-s-army-chief-says-strategy-overhaul-is-needed-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 20:31:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
